## Radio System

The radio system provides communication between the pilot and the drone.

This platform uses the FlySky i6 transmitter and receiver pair because it is:

- Affordable
- Reliable
- Beginner friendly
- Widely available
- Easy to configure

For a regular drone platform, the FlySky system provides more than enough functionality for:

- Stable control
- Learning
- Testing
- Tuning
- Experimentation

It also keeps the overall build cost practical while still maintaining dependable communication during flight.

